49,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T10:23:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>當我冇生過你啦<br />\n/<br />\n我都唔知點解生左你出黎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46371ec4a310399394ab0adf81d397ed4eb9b63a","tid":16093,"uid":15558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T10:35:58.000Z","msg":"媽：係咪你拎左屋企啲錢<br />\n<br />\n我：無呀<br />\n<br />\n媽：點解要拎屋企啲錢<br />\n<br />\n我：我真係無呀 你自己揾清楚先啦<br />\n<br />\n媽：你唔夠錢可以問我..點解要..（下刪一千字）<br />\n<br />\n講左幾次居然仲認為我偷屋企錢 心都淡鳩哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到而家都覺得比齊家用當盡左本份<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外有一次hurt得最深係有朝早呀媽無啦啦問我係咪我ex偷左佢枝護膚來用 我話佢肯定唔會 佢黑哂臉話以後帶小點佢上來屋企，又係講啲好難聽既說話，話咩成枝無理由唔見左，係咪佢拎左去自己用，跟住佢就頭也不回去左番工<br />\n<br />\n跟住我響佢床邊「LA」位影左張相比佢，打左段千字文比佢，講番點解要懷疑我，甚至係懷疑我女朋友<br />\n<br />\n個陣真係萬念俱灰。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ba6907fdcb57de4c4f352e8f48c380e50601026","tid":16093,"uid":8902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T10:41:25.000Z","msg":"渣ga"},{"pid":"8a9a8bd5da3387275ab304dfba416c26e8428eb9","tid":16093,"uid":35384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T10:43:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老豆: 我生您出黎架，無我您乜都唔係啊，您出糧成份糧比晒我都係應份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 聽過<br />\n咁叻佢就自己十月懷胎生一個 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b5e923d46a568aa3e313f7bd68dba9fa3f4951e","tid":16093,"uid":20470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T10:49:37.000Z","msg":"媽：咁多年扮有母愛 好攰喇我"},{"pid":"39a54e17539de16e39340ccba2af31b15dd96fa6","tid":16093,"uid":25249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T10:49:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>渣ga</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/asse